	   <tr><td colspan=2>I can never seem to reason why there aren't more Dark Elf wizards. We have good int, agi, and dex. Str is better than most lighties. Being evil isn't so bad. Its a plus. Don't have to worry about faction like the lighties at later levels. (btw I reccomend worshiping Solusek Ro or being Agnostic)<br><br>The wizard guild is in the middle Neriak zone. Its easy to find, or it gets that way after visiting it many times. As a wiz you don't have to worry about being killed by gaurds while traveling as much. You can avoid most boats. Travel is very fast.<br><br>Really the first 12 levels are a wizards worst so here are places to hunt. 1-4 I like to go to the newbie area of Nro and kill things. Nuke, then melee a bit, then nuke. At 5 or 4 (if you are courageous or buffed) I like to venture to the desert and kill Jackals and Orcs till 6 or 7. <br>From 6 - 8 our power is discouraging so get a group and just hang on. <br><br>8 is a small taste of power. Use the shock. Bolts are bad for a few reasons. 8-9 stay in Nro and get a partner or small group. Kill those giant spiders and scarabs. Loot is acceptable but minimal compared to some. 9-12 I went to East Commons and killed the Deathfist orcs in groups. Sell the belts and your cash situation should be fine. <br><br>At 12 with spells solo'n is a decent option. Dervs are an option. Caimans/crocs in Oasis is an option.<br><br>If you are on Ayonae Ro and want some tips or help starting out send me a tell!<br>&nbsp;<br>Slayyer 46 Dark Elf <br>Doldar 33 Human Monk</td></tr>
