	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well it seems that Verant has decided that we have to swim all the time to get the nicest items...&nbsp;&nbsp;The parts to Staff of the Wheel are all underwater and part of the epic quest involves going to Kedge Keep.  Just as a bit of advice, I would suggest everyone go get a Fishbone Earring.  It holds unlimited charges of enduring breath and if any new wizard quests come up I am sure that swimming will be a large part of it.  The earring is hardly ever seen for sale but it drops off of a lvl 29 fisherman named Hadden in Qeynos Hills.  Killing him can cause great trouble with your faction in Qeynos, so it is advisable to find a friend that is already KOS there to get it for you.  You should almost consider this earring part of your Ice Comet Quest and Epic Quest.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
